iente Più Intelligente</h2><p class="text-xl text-slate-600 leading-relaxed max-w-xl">Crea un&#x27;esperienza sanitaria digitale completa che mette i pazienti in controllo del loro percorso di cura riducendo al contempo il tuo carico amministrativo.</p></div><div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8"><div class="space-y-4"><div class="flex items-start gap-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-file-text h-6 w-6 text-green-muted flex-shrink-0 mt-1" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M15 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V7Z"></path><path d="M14 2v4a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h4"></path><path d="M10 9H8"></path><path d="M16 13H8"></path><path d="M16 17H8"></path></svg><div><h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-1">Accesso Completo al Profilo Sanitario</h3><p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Un unico hub sicuro di informazioni sanitarie</p></div></div></div><div class="space-y-4"><div class="flex items-start gap-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-calendar h-6 w-6 text-green-muted flex-shrink-0 mt-1" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M8 2v4"></path><path d="M16 2v4"></path><rect width="18" height="18" x="3" y="4" rx="2"></rect><path d="M3 10h18"></path></svg><div><h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-1">Gestione Facile degli Appuntamenti</h3><p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Integrazione di pianificazione in tempo reale disponibile</p></div></div></div><div class="space-y-4"><div class="flex items-start gap-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-credit-card h-6 w-6 text-gr